---

import Header from '../../components/Header'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer'
import RequestQuoteForm from '../../components/RequestQuoteForm'
import whitePhone from '../../assets/white-phone.svg'
import yardSign from '../../assets/yard-sign-Opt.jpg'
import love from '../../assets/love.svg'

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" href="../AlderFavicon.png" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
        <meta name="description" content="For home security Alabama, the most important choice you can make is which company to choose. Alder Home Security will keep families safe, happy, and secure." />
		<title>Home Security Alabama | Alder Home Security</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-white w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center">

        <Header path='/states/alabama' client:load />

        <br/>

        <div class="w-full h-[325px] bg-cover bg-center max-w-6xl" style={{
            backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto/v1557270355/Alabama.jpg")'
        }}>
        <div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col items-center gap-8 justify-center bg-neutral-800/[.50]">

            <h1 class="text-white font-medium w-4/5 md:w-1/2 text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl text-center">Best Home Security Alabama</h1>

            <a href="tel:800-710-1289" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 transition duration-100 py-2 px-4 rounded-3xl border-2 z-10 border-white">
                <img alt="phone icon" src={whitePhone}/>
                <p class="text-white text-[15px]">Call Now 800-710-1289</p>
            </a>
            
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl py-20 px-4 bg-white flex justify-center items-center ">

            <p class="text-[#58585B] leading-7 w-full md:w-4/5 lg:w-2/3 text-center">Every person in every state needs comfort, safety, and the peace of mind that comes with having security systems. That’s where Alder Home Security comes in. At Alder, we look to care for people across the United States. In Alabama, we provide hundreds of happy families the comfort of knowing they have monitoring for their homes with our smart home alarm systems.</p>

        </div>

        <RequestQuoteForm client:load bg_color="bg-[#61798F]" />

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl bg-cover" style={{
            backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto/v1557271904/Map_Screen_Shot.png")'
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-[#297CA3]/[.50] flex flex-col items-center py-4 px-6 gap-4 justify-evenly">
                <h2 class="flex flex-row items-center text-2xl sm:text-6xl text-white font-medium gap-2 bg-neutral-800/[.75] p-2 rounded-xl ">WE <img alt="heart" class=" w-[30px] h-[30px] sm:w-[65px] sm:h-[65px]" src={love} /> ALABAMA </h2>

                <p class="text-white bg-neutral-800/[.85] text-sm md:text-base w-full md:w-2/3 p-4 leading-6 ">Alabama is one of the states where we do our best work. The people are friendly, kind, and neighbors look out for each other. People from Alabama recognize the importance of caring for their families and do everything in their power to keep their families safe. This is why Alder is such a popular choice for home security in Alabama. We put your families first to give you the best home security systems on the market to ensure that you’re protected night and day. All of our systems are made with the family in mind. Our security monitoring systems are made, so they’re easy to understand and easy to manage. We want to give home security Alabama a great name that our customers can count on.</p>
        </div>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-cover bg-center " style={{
            backgroundImage: `url(${yardSign})`
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-neutral-800/[.75] md:bg-neutral-800/[.45] flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 py-8 px-4 md:px-12">

            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl">Working Hard to bring</h3>

            <h3 class="text-white text-4xl font-medium">Alabama Peace of Mind</h3>

            <p class="text-white text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium md:w-1/2 leading-6">Our products are made with our customer’s concerns in mind. For home security Alabama, we ensure that you have protection on the go. That’s why we’ve made home security mobile. WIth our home security, you can now connect to it through your phone to make sure that your home is protected no matter where you are in the world. We make your Smart home even better by allowing you to interact with it. You can lock the doors from the office or make sure that the security systems were turned on after you left. Your home security systems are our responsibility, and it is our goal to help you to have peace of mind wherever you’re at.</p>

        </div>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-full h-[250px] bg-cover" style={{
                backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/v1557333574/simple.jpg")',
                backgroundPosition: "center 85%"
            }} />

            <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 md:gap-0 md:flex-row px-4 py-12 ">

                <div class=" w-full md:w-[25%] flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-4">
                    <h3 class="text-[#58585B] font-medium text-2xl text-center md:text-left ">Local Home Security Monitoring in Alabama </h3>

                    <p class="text-[#58585B] text-xl text-start" >From Alder</p>
                </div>

                <p class="text-[#58585B] text-sm leading-6 w-full md:w-[65%] " >
                    We work to give local homes in Alabama constant home security monitoring. This will ensure constant safety for you, your family, and your dog that’s left at home all day. Safety is something that every family who has home security Alabama deserves. Our smart home alarm will alert you whenever an alarm is triggered at your home. You have complete control over the monitoring of the alarm and can contact the police when our alarm systems notify you. One of the benefits of having a Smart Home is that you’re in control. Having a Smart Home gives you the safety and the satisfaction knowing that you’re in good hands. Get home security Alabama with Alder, and we’ll take care of you and your family.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>
        
    
        <Footer />

    </body>
</html>